    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >QQ群：2151021832</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >B站/微博/小红书：@鸟兀工作室</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258560/extras/52e13a7786059154048ade4081de0ce1.avif?t=1771754040\" width=615 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >很久很久以前，一位传奇魔法师牺牲了自己并用魔法阵封印了魔王，保住了王国。多年过去，不知从何时起，国王频繁下令无故抓走平民，而被抓走的人也不知被送去了哪里，也再没有人见过他们！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >突然有一天，魔法阵出现松动，魔王成功逃出了牢笼，并附身到了冒险者身上。作为魔王化身的你，能否接纳自己的新身份？又能否发现国王的阴谋？是拯救“同胞”？还是消灭“异类”？是善？是恶？仅在一念之间...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258560/extras/d0f62bb823a2e7393f0939ba92995b7a.avif?t=1771754040\" width=615 height=150 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了单人游玩，双人亦可组队战斗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目前，游戏已支持远程同乐和本地双人合作，快叫上你的小伙伴一起冒险吧！神秘人的阴谋等你揭晓！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258560/extras/81de42e6e79e0b6953867372515de2bf.poster.avif?t=1771754040\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258560/extras/81de42e6e79e0b6953867372515de2bf.webm?t=1771754040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258560/extras/81de42e6e79e0b6953867372515de2bf.mp4?t=1771754040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258560/extras/5dea82946f723147201a801593767458.avif?t=1771754040\" width=615 height=150 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1000+构筑机制，无限组合。对纯数值成长的体验说No！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随意自由组合流派，相互联动游戏机制，激烈的化学反应保证每局游戏体验绝不重复！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258560/extras/e2b788cff362c64459a170cf3bf0bc4f.poster.avif?t=1771754040\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258560/extras/e2b788cff362c64459a170cf3bf0bc4f.webm?t=1771754040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258560/extras/e2b788cff362c64459a170cf3bf0bc4f.mp4?t=1771754040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258560/extras/87f4906a8cdfa049b9e228de831e31f9.avif?t=1771754040\" width=615 height=150 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可根据自身需要自由选择路线分支！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >宝箱房，挑战房，稀有天赋待你找寻，使你的构筑更加强力！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258560/extras/0d54d89a5582c9b730d354782c7851f2.poster.avif?t=1771754040\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258560/extras/0d54d89a5582c9b730d354782c7851f2.webm?t=1771754040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258560/extras/0d54d89a5582c9b730d354782c7851f2.mp4?t=1771754040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
